This file contains a brief description of Knotter releases,
showing when features have been added to the program.

Knotter 0.3.0 (beta) - Ongoing development
--------------------
* Grid
* I8n
* Customization

Knotter 0.2.0 (beta)
---------------------
* Zooming
* Copy/Paste
* Fixed some crashes

Knotter 0.1.0 (alpha)
---------------------
First public release
* Basic Editing
* Open/Save
* Undo/Redo
* Style
* SVG Export
